---
title: Plant-Based Mince & Basil Pesto Spaghetti with Leek & Parmesan Cheese
description: A spaghetti dinner demands a checkered tablecloth, candles and the freshest ingredients to pull off a dinner that will win hearts. To achieve this, cook up plant-based mince in a tomato sauce, with leek and carrot and toss through with basil pesto.
